T10TD4168E:181b-27: khrus kyi gtam ste bdun pa'o /
T10TD4168E:181b-29: // / khrus byed lha yi bu mo mchog / rked ldan brla dang nu ma rgyas //

T10TD4168E:181b-47: rin chen sna bdun rnams dang ni //

T10TD4168E:182a-2: kha dog sna tshogs dri zhim pa'i //

T10TD4168E:182a-4: gdugs mdzes sna tshogs dar gyis brgyan //
T10TD4168E:182a-5: mchod rten rnams la phul ba yis //
T10TD4168E:182a-6: 'khor los sgyur ba sa skyong ba //

T10TD4168E:182a-11: gling bzhi yi ni 'khor los sgyur //
T10TD4168E:182a-12: sa rnams ma lus skyong bar byed //
T10TD4168E:182a-13: de dag bde gshegs sku gdung la //
T10TD4168E:182a-14: me tog gdugs phul 'bras bu yin //
T10TD4168E:182a-15: gdugs phul ba'i gtam ste dgu pa'o /
T10TD4168E:182a-17: // / bde bar gshegs pa'i 'khrungs gnas dang //

T10TD4168E:182a-26: mi dbang gling bzhi rnams su ni //

T10TD4168E:182a-33: rgya mtshos gtugs pa'i sa rnams ni //

T10TD4168E:182a-36: ring bsrel dang bcas gus pas 'thob //
T10TD4168E:182a-37: ring bsrel gyi gtam ste bcu pa'o /
T10TD4168E:182a-39: // / bde bar gshegs pa mchog rnams kyi //
T10TD4168E:182a-40: pho brang mchog ni brgyan byed pa //
T10TD4168E:182a-41: gser gyi mdog dang ldan 'gyur zhing //
T10TD4168E:182a-42: nad rnams kun las grol bar 'gyur //
T10TD4168E:182a-43: lha dang mi las khyad 'phags shing //
T10TD4168E:182a-44: nyi ma'i 'khor lo lta bur mdzes //
T10TD4168E:182a-45: nor dang gser ni mang ba dang //
T10TD4168E:182a-46: rgyal po'i rigs kyi rgyal bar 'gyur //
T10TD4168E:182a-47: 'jig rten gsum gyis mchod pa yi //
T10TD4168E:182a-48: sangs rgyas la ni gang zhig 'dir //

T10TD4168E:182b-0: @182b sna tshogs nad kyi 'jigs las grol //
T10TD4168E:182b-1: gang yin de yis skad cig thob //
T10TD4168E:182b-2: bde gshegs mandal byed de dag / pha rol phyin drug thob 'gyur te //
T10TD4168E:182b-3: chu dang sa bsres btang sbyin pa //
T10TD4168E:182b-4: grog mo sogs sel tshul khrims te //
T10TD4168E:182b-5: bsres nas nyes pa bzod pa yin //
T10TD4168E:182b-7: / skad cig de las rtse gcig tu //
T10TD4168E:182b-8: sems 'dzin byed pa bsam gtan yin //
T10TD4168E:182b-9: legs par gzob pa shes rab po //
T10TD4168E:182b-10: sna tshogs bsod nams kyis brgyan la //
T10TD4168E:182b-11: sa gzhi bris pa 'brul byed pa //
T10TD4168E:182b-12: lha yi bde ba thams cad dang //
T10TD4168E:182b-13: longs spyod mchog dang ldan 'gyur zhing //
T10TD4168E:182b-14: mir skyes gser las lhag pa yi //
T10TD4168E:182b-15: kha dog dang ldan mdzes pa dang //
T10TD4168E:182b-16: padma'i mdog ltar yan lag tshang //
T10TD4168E:182b-17: mig ni dkyus ring mdzes par 'gyur //
T10TD4168E:182b-18: mandal gyi gtam ste bcu gcig pa'o /
T10TD4168E:182b-21: 'od gsal kha dog dri bzang ldan //
T10TD4168E:182b-22: ro zhim reg na bde ba dang ;
T10TD4168E:182b-23: / lha dang mi yi khang bzangs na //
T10TD4168E:182b-24: 'od gsal gser gyi gzhong pa ru //
T10TD4168E:182b-25: lha yi bdud rtsis bkang za ba //
T10TD4168E:182b-26: de dag sangs rgyas la sogs pa'i //
T10TD4168E:182b-27: dge 'dun yul du lhags pa la //
T10TD4168E:182b-28: zhal zas drangs pa'i 'bras bu yin //
T10TD4168E:182b-29: rdo rje gdan la bzhugs nas ni //
T10TD4168E:182b-30: 'dod pa'i dgra dang bcas pa yi//
T10TD4168E:182b-31: tshogs ni byams pas des 'pham mdzad //
T10TD4168E:182b-32: gang zhig mthar thug dka' ba'i yul //
T10TD4168E:182b-33: mtha' med par ni spyod 'gyur ba'i //
T10TD4168E:182b-34: nyon mongs dka' ba'i dgra las rgyal //
T10TD4168E:182b-35: phung po'i bdud kyang rab bcom nas //
T10TD4168E:182b-36: 'chi bdag bdud la mnga' brnyes pa //
T10TD4168E:182b-37: zhal zas phul bar gyur pas yin //
T10TD4168E:182b-38: ro rnams bro ba'i mchog dang ni //
T10TD4168E:182b-39: yan lag tshang zhing yongs rdzogs ldan //
T10TD4168E:182b-40: bde zhing dpal ldan stobs dang ldan //
T10TD4168E:182b-41: tshe dang stobs dang kha dog dang //
T10TD4168E:182b-42: gzugs bzang ba dang ldan pa ni //
T10TD4168E:182b-43: mkhas pas zas mchog btang las byung //
T10TD4168E:182b-44: stobs dang brtson 'grus ldan pa yi //
T10TD4168E:182b-45: rnam grangs las ni nges par rgyal //
T10TD4168E:182b-46: yang dag dpal thob mi dbang gis //
T10TD4168E:182b-47: ro ldan kha zas longs spyod pa //
T10TD4168E:182b-48: rtag tu zas mchog sbyin des yin //
T10TD4168E:182b-49: zas kyi gtam ste bcu gnyis pa'o /
T10TD4168E:182b-51: // / g-yo zhing autpal gyis bsgos pa //
T10TD4168E:182b-52: dri med padma r'a ga bzhin //
T10TD4168E:182b-53: yid 'ong gser gyi snod du blugs//
T10TD4168E:183a-0: @183a * // dri zhim tsandan gyis bsgos mngar //
T10TD4168E:183a-2: cung zad mig ni zangs mdog 'dra //
T10TD4168E:183a-3: glu len sgra dang nges ldan pa'i //
T10TD4168E:183a-4: mi mchog de rnams skom rnams ni //
T10TD4168E:183a-5: sbyin pa byin pa'i 'bras bu yin //
T10TD4168E:183a-7: rin chen mchog rnams kyis spras pa'i //
T10TD4168E:183a-8: gser gyi snod ni gang yin par //
T10TD4168E:183a-9: lha gang lha yi bu mo ni //
T10TD4168E:183a-10: brang gi dkyil na nu ma ni //
T10TD4168E:183a-11: bum pa lta bu'i 'bur ldan pa'i //
T10TD4168E:183a-12: rab mdzes gcugs dang lhan cig tu //
T10TD4168E:183a-13: sbrang rtsi ltar mngar btung 'thung ba //

T10TD4168E:183a-16: 'bras bu yin par mkhas rnams gsungs //
T10TD4168E:183a-17: gang zhig kha dog dri zhim sogs //
T10TD4168E:183a-18: tshogs ldan skom pa'i sdug bsngal sel //

T10TD4168E:183a-22: zla ba'i 'od zer dang ldan pa'i //

T10TD4168E:183a-24: gus par dge 'dun la phul bas //
T10TD4168E:183a-25: pha rol gyi ni skye gnas su //
T10TD4168E:183a-26: lha yi btung ba thob par 'gyur //
T10TD4168E:183a-27: mngar zhim mngar mchog gus pa yis //
T10TD4168E:183a-28: btung ba tshogs mchog la phul bas //
T10TD4168E:183a-29: lha dang mi yi gnas rnams su //
T10TD4168E:183a-30: lha yi bu mo mchog rnams dang //
T10TD4168E:183a-31: yun ring btung ba lhan cig 'thung //
T10TD4168E:183a-32: gang zhig sa gnas mi rnams kyis //

T10TD4168E:183a-35: 'khor ba'i ri khrod gnas pa ni //
T10TD4168E:183a-36: rtag tu btung ba 'ang zhim bzang thob //
T10TD4168E:183a-37: btung ba'i gtam ste bcu gsum pa'o /
T10TD4168E:183a-39: // / gang zhig sdo ser ljang dmar dkar ;

T10TD4168E:183a-44: bsngags pa'i gos mchog thob par 'gyur //
T10TD4168E:183a-45: gang zhig dge 'dun mchog sogs la //
T10TD4168E:183a-46: gang zhig dad dang gus pa yis //
T10TD4168E:183a-47: gos kyi phreng ba 'bul byed pa ;

T10TD4168E:183b-8: // / me tog bzang po dge 'dun la //
T10TD4168E:183b-9: rab tu 'thor zhing mchod byed pa //
T10TD4168E:183b-10: brgya byin las lhag longs spyod ldan //
T10TD4168E:183b-11: padma'i dbang po lta bur mdzes //
T10TD4168E:183b-12: mchog tu grags pa dang ldan zhing //

T10TD4168E:183b-21: mig ni dri med dkyus ring mdzes //
T10TD4168E:183b-22: bee d'urya dang mu tig dang //
T10TD4168E:183b-23: rin po che yis yan lag brgyan //
T10TD4168E:183b-24: lus kun ku sha'i gos kyis g-yogs //
T10TD4168E:183b-25: skye ba kun du mi yi mchog / gzugs dang ldan par gyur pa ni //
T10TD4168E:183b-26: dge 'dun dri bzang phul ba yin //
T10TD4168E:183b-27: sna tshogs pa yi sman rnams ni //
T10TD4168E:183b-28: de dag dge 'dun la phul bas //
T10TD4168E:183b-29: mdze la sogs pa'i nad rnams kyi //
T10TD4168E:183b-30: sdug bsngal mi bzad pa las grol //
T10TD4168E:183b-31: bzhin ni mdzes shing gser rnams dang //
T10TD4168E:183b-32: mnyam zhing kha dog yid du 'ong //
T10TD4168E:183b-33: rgyal po yi ni 'tshe ba rnams //
T10TD4168E:183b-34: gang yin pa dang bral ba thob //
T10TD4168E:183b-35: me tog la sogs pa'i gtam ste bco lnga pa'o /
T10TD4168E:183b-37: // / sa bdag 'khor los sgyur gang la //
T10TD4168E:183b-38: thal mo sbyar ba byas nas ni //

T10TD4168E:183b-46: rta dang glang pos rgyu byed pa //
T10TD4168E:183b-47: de dag bla ma 'phags pa la //
T10TD4168E:183b-48: legs par phyag ni byas pas yin //
T10TD4168E:183b-49: snyan pa yis ni khyab 'gyur zhing ;
T10TD4168E:183b-50: / nges par legs par 'dzin pa dang //
T10TD4168E:183b-51: gsal bar byed pa'i 'od kyis ni //
T10TD4168E:183b-52: sdug bsngal thams cad spong byed cing //
T10TD4168E:183b-53: nad ni thams cad 'joms par byed //
T10TD4168E:183b-55: mi dbang gis ni rgyun du 'gyur //
T10TD4168E:183b-56: 'bras bu dpal dang ldan pa yang //
T10TD4168E:184a-2: 'khor los sgyur rgyal stobs grags ldan //

T10TD4168E:184a-4: rgyal 'gyur sa stengs gtso po de //

T10TD4168E:184a-9: mkhas pas sangs rgyas phyag bya zhing //

T10TD4168E:184a-11: phyag gcig 'tshal bar gyur pa yis //
T10TD4168E:184a-12: 'khor ba spong ba'i rgyu thob cing //
T10TD4168E:184a-14: de ltar su zhig phyag mi byed //

T10TD4168E:184a-18: // / krishna sa ra ltar mdzes gzugs //

T10TD4168E:184a-26: shin tu 'bras bu mngon yin par //
T10TD4168E:184a-27: yang dag rdzogs sangs rin chen gsungs //
T10TD4168E:184a-28: 'bar zhing me lce rgyas dang ldan //
T10TD4168E:184a-29: khang pa'i nang du me 'bar gsal //

T10TD4168E:184a-34: gsal zhing rab tu 'bar gyur dang //
T10TD4168E:184a-35: dri za lha min mi 'am ci //
